ygData.msgSnippet: Bows and arrows RULE!!  With a little bit of work you can get your fletching skill up high enough to make more arrows than you know what to do with, or heck
ygData.messageBody:
Bows and arrows RULE!! With a little bit of work you can get your fletching
skill up high enough to make more arrows than you know what to do with, or
heck they only cost 1sp at the dealer. 9 points damage every time with an
archery skill of only 35 adds up in the long run.


For the Honor and Glory of Rallos Zek;

Patty of Halas
